svg.style: width: 100%; height: 100%; position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 0px; overflow: visible;

text.style: font-size: 30px; fill: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: "Amatic SC"; font-weight: 700; white-space: pre-wrap; opacity: 1;

tspan.style: font-size: 30px; color: rgb(32, 32, 32); font-family: "Amatic SC"; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0px; text-transform: uppercase;

rect.style: fill: none; stroke-miterlimit: 10; stroke-width: 0; display: none;

path.style: fill: none; stroke-miterlimit: 10; stroke-width: 0; display: block;
